data.description: Welcome to 14635 Crossway Rd, a one-of-a-kind luxury home nestled in the prestigious Manor Park community of Rockville, Maryland. This exquisitely renovated residence is a masterpiece of design and craftsmanship, boasting high ceilings and open spaces that seamlessly connect to offer an unparalleled living experience. Step into a world where every detail has been thoughtfully curated to impress the most discerning buyer. The heart of this home is the expansive kitchen, outfitted with white quartz countertops, and modern, stylish finishes. The flooring and designer touches throughout create an inviting space for both chef-grade cooking and casual entertaining. The formal living room adjoins the office and dining spaces for an entertainer's flow that is sure to delight all who visit. The Great room, with its soaring 20ft ceilings and dual sets of double doors leading to the back patio, is a spectacular sight. The large fireplace with a custom mantel enhances the ambiance, making it the perfect spot for gatherings or a serene evening by the fire. Experience exemplary luxury with the first-floor master bedroom, featuring soaring ceilings, recessed lighting, and an ensuite bath. Upstairs, a loft, three large bedrooms and two fully renovated baths await, alongside a flexible space wonderful for fitness, play or study and is connected to the mudroom below by a spiral staircase. The top floor offers additional space, a potential fifth bedroom, a fourth full bath, and ample storage. The outdoor oasis is a true highlight, featuring a heated mineral water pool with waterfalls, multi-tiered flagstone patios, professional landscaping, and sprawling yard space, creating an idyllic private retreat. Located just steps from Manor Country Club, enjoy access to championship golf courses, delectable dining, casual pub, multiple swimming pools, and tennis courts.  Ask for details about membership. This is more than a home; it's a lifestyle in a community with much to offer. Don't miss the opportunity to own this unique gem at 14635 Crossway Rd, where luxury living and attention to detail converge in a setting that is nothing short of spectacular. Short sale is managed by an experienced short sale team.
